# CV Portfolio ÔÇö Cursor Rules

## Project Context

**Owner:** Jawdat Abdullah  
**Stack:** Vite + React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + Redux Toolkit + i18next  
**Repo:** https://github.com/jawdat89/cv  
**Reference docs:** `agent/` folder (design system, copy, roadmap)

## Core Positioning

> "I build practical software at the intersection of ERP, logistics, automation, and modern web development."

The site should feel **modern, industrial, trustworthy, and enterprise-focused** ÔÇö not like a generic developer template.

---

## Design System (Strict)

### Colors ÔÇö use ONLY these via `brand-*` Tailwind tokens or `src/lib/theme.ts`

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| Background | `#0F172A` | Page background (`brand-bg`) |
| Surface | `#1F2937` | Cards, nav (`brand-surface`) |
| Text Primary | `#F9FAFB` | Headings, body (`brand-text`) |
| Text Secondary | `#9CA3AF` | Subtitles, meta (`brand-muted`) |
| Accent | `#3B82F6` | CTAs, links (`brand-accent`) |
| Teal | `#14B8A6` | Alternative accent (`brand-teal`) |
| Highlight | `#F59E0B` | Sparingly (`brand-highlight`) |

### Typography (Inter font)

- h1: `3.5rem` ÔÇö Hero name only
- h2: `2.5rem` ÔÇö Section titles
- h3: `1.75rem` ÔÇö Subsection titles
- h4: `1.25rem` ÔÇö Card titles
- body: `1rem`
- small: `0.875rem`

### Spacing ÔÇö 8px base scale

8, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96 px ÔÇö no arbitrary values.

### Components

Use shared UI in `src/components/ui/`:
- **Card** ÔÇö surface bg, subtle border, 24px padding, 2px hover lift
- **Button** ÔÇö primary (filled accent) and secondary (outlined) only
- **Badge** ÔÇö tech stack tags, no percentage bars
- **Section** ÔÇö max-width 1200px, consistent vertical padding

---

## Content Rules

Approved copy lives in `src/i18n/locales/en.json` (sourced from `agent/.homepage_copy.md`, `agent/.section_rewrite.md`).

- **Contact details** appear ONLY in the Contact section
- **About text** appears ONLY in the About section
- **Skills** use grouped badges ÔÇö NO percentage bars
- **Experience** uses outcome-focused bullet lists
- **Projects** lead with business-oriented descriptions

### Section Order

1. Hero Ôćĺ 2. What I Bring Ôćĺ 3. About Ôćĺ 4. Featured Projects Ôćĺ 5. Experience Ôćĺ 6. Skills Ôćĺ 7. Education & Certifications Ôćĺ 8. Languages Ôćĺ 9. Contact

---

## Code Standards

- TypeScript strict mode ÔÇö no `any`
- Components under 200 lines; split if larger
- Use `@/` path aliases
- Semantic HTML: `nav`, `main`, `section`, proper heading hierarchy (h1 Ôćĺ h2 Ôćĺ h3)
- ARIA labels on all interactive elements
- WCAG AA color contrast minimum
- Support keyboard navigation and `prefers-reduced-motion`

---

## Animation Guidelines

Allowed:
- Fade in on scroll (~300ms)
- Card hover lift (2px, 200ms)
- Button hover (150ms)

NOT allowed:
- Parallax, heavy motion, auto-playing animations, bright gradients, excessive glows

---

## i18n

- English (`en.json`) is the source of truth for approved copy
- Add new keys to `en.json` first; update `he.json` and `ar.json` when translating
- Use `t()` with `returnObjects: true` for arrays (bullets, skill lists)

---

## File Structure

```
src/
  components/ui/     # Card, Button, Badge, Section
  lib/theme.ts       # Design tokens
  pages/dashboard/   # Dashboard sections
  i18n/locales/      # Translations
  store/             # Redux state
agent/               # Design docs and Cursor prompts (reference only)
```

---

## Implementation Phases

1. **Foundation** ÔÇö theme, Tailwind, base components Ôťů
2. **Content** ÔÇö Hero, Value Prop, About, Skills refactor
3. **Advanced** ÔÇö Projects, Experience, Education, Contact
4. **Polish** ÔÇö animations, responsive audit, accessibility, Lighthouse 90+

See `agent/.CURSOR_GUIDE.md` and `agent/.cursor-prompts.md` for detailed prompts.

---

## Do NOT

- Introduce colors outside the approved palette
- Add skill percentage bars or ratings
- Duplicate contact info across sections
- Use Next.js patterns (this is Vite, not Next.js)
- Over-engineer abstractions for one-off use cases
